1.0.0.name: wordpress/wp-additions-pagination
1.0.0.description: This plugin converts Wordpress Admin Pagination (Posts, Pages, Comments, Users) to an AJAX Slider System. Now a it is possible to easily page through thousands of rows of information faster than every before, making your Wordpress Administration that much easier!
